data.meta_description: Debenhams - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Debenhams is a British multinational retailer operating department stores in the UK, Ireland, and Denmark. It was founded in the 18th century and now has 178 store locations. Debenhams sells clothing, home goods, and furniture. In 1993, it introduced its 'Designers at Debenhams' brand range. Stores also contain concessions from other retailers. Debenhams operates online stores and mobile apps. It provides financial services like credit cards and operates bureaux de change in some stores.
